* Content:
============

Folder contains a program that simulates the producer - consumer
problem using shared memory and system V semaphore.

    Included files:
	1)	producer.c		source code for producer process
		consumer.c		source code for consumer process

	2) 	lib_sem.h		a library of semaphore
		lib_sem.c		handling functions

	3)	lib_shm.h		a library of shared memory
		lib_shm.c		handling functions

	4)	producer.txt		text file containing producer
                            		material

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* How to run:
=========================

Catalog contains Makefile for compiling and running the program

-> To compile the program using static library, type make main
-> To compile the program using dynamic library (shared object),
	type make mainSO
-> To run the program, type make run
-> For after-usage-clean, type make clean
